E-commerce Website
 About the Project

This project is a simple E-commerce Website built as part of my web development major project. The idea behind it is to create a platform where users can easily browse products, add them to their cart, and place orders online.

While working on this project, I focused on making the interface clean and easy to use, along with implementing the core functionality that makes an online store actually work behind the scenes.

 What Users Can Do
Create an account and log in
Browse different products on the dashboard
View detailed information about each product
Add products to their cart
Place orders using Cash on Delivery
View their previous orders
Get a confirmation once an order is placed

What Admin Can Do
Log in securely to the admin panel
Add new products to the website
View all orders placed by users
Check customer details
Manage the overall store
